( 35 )
Bosmina ( Liederobosmina ) huaronensis Delachaux, 1918
. Not recorded in Chilean literature, but definitively present in many localities in Chile (A.A. Kotov, unpublished). A taxon which is widely ditributed in the Americas (
Paggi 1979
;
De Melo & Hebert 1994
;
Elías-Gutiérrez et al. 2008
).
